{"word":"εὐήμερος","slug":"εὐήμερος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>εὐήμερος</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:ἡμέρα'><el>ἡμέρα</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>of a fine day</i>, <el>εὐ. φάος</el> <i>a happy</i> day, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>enjoying a lucky day, cheerful, happy</i>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}